msgid "Upgrading to version 2.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/upgrading-to-2.0.rst:4
msgid ""
"To upgrade an early edition of Mattermost to the latest edition, you must"
" first upgrade in a specific sequence until you get to version 2.0.0. "
"After that, you must upgrade to version 3.0.3, and from there you can "
"upgrade directly to the latest Mattermost version."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/upgrading-to-2.0.rst:6
msgid ""
"Read these instructions carefully from start to finish. Make sure that "
"you understand each step before starting the upgrade. If you have "
"questions or concerns, you can ask on the Mattermost forum at "
"https://forum.mattermost.org/."
msgstr ""

